SIZE=(18,67), ORIENT=(02,07)
WINDOW BOX
EASEL ON


                   Incentive Balance Option - Help

    Used to qualify a relationship based on the primary account
    meeting a required balance, combined balances meeting
    a required balance, or individual balances meeting a
    required balance.  This option determines if one or all
    requirements must be met for a relationship to qualify
    for an incentive.  Valid entries are:

      A  Use the 'and' condition for incentive balance
         decisions.
      O  Use the 'or' condition for incentive balance
         decisions.
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M01054S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
